{"tid":646852,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【英超巴菲特】雲加的價值投資法","createTime":"2018-04-29T11:40:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-29T13:41:49.000Z","uid":64863,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"81c18a23f3a5137630d484f539653b33479e3374","tid":646852,"uid":64863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T11:40:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/nowwwhatapp/posts/1915441758697260:0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnowwwhatapp%2Fposts%2F1915441758697260%3A0&d=MfFOQdkPCtCIbPE6r2e4gTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=ffc8ef07\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/nowwwhatapp/posts/1915441758697260:0</a><br />\n<br />\n【英超巴菲特&mdash;雲加】<br />\n<br />\n雲加是英超史上執教時間最長的英超領隊。於今個賽季完結後離任教練，結束22年執教阿仙奴的生涯。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">最近阿仙奴公佈近半年業績，利潤增長了超過一倍。一如以往，主要收入是來自賣球員，包括中場阿歷士張伯倫、左閘基蘭基比斯等，進賬了5840萬鎊，稅前利潤由2016年的1260萬鎊，激增至2510萬鎊。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n小編可以說一下，太過重視一次性收益會有咩後果。<br />\n<br />\n雲加賣主力球員，固然可以賺取非常高的利潤。然而這是一次性的收入，都犧牲了以後爭奪英超的機會和歐聯的機會(*16年英超冠軍李斯特城獲獎金9300萬鎊; 皇馬上季衛冕歐聯所獲金額為7260萬鎊)。當然這都是一個機會成本取捨。<br />\n<br />\n而雲加作為一個經濟學家，都深深明白到邊際利潤。由於歷史原因，英超頭四已經可以直入歐聯，而歐聯既獎金較歐霸獎金豐厚（歐聯盃小組賽保底獎金720萬歐元，歐霸100萬歐元），所以打入前四已經非常有著數。<br />\n<br />\n即使拎第一，其實都係同第四係無分別，都係拎咁多錢，又何必再用咁多錢去買人，增加個cost，去換取不成正比既利潤?<br />\n<br />\n另一個解釋，雲加明白到拎英超同歐聯既ROI(return on investment)唔高，即使拎到冠軍，分分鐘獎金都cover唔到買人既支出。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">所以雲加既定位其實係成為一間「足球學校」，專門選出有潛力既青訓，低價買入，重點培育，成材後就高價賣出，一如股市上既價值投資法。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">事後睇反，雲加其實都係一個英超巴菲特。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雲加又贏一<br />\n<br />\n你又點睇雲加一直以來的策略呢?<br />\n你又點睇今晚曼聯對阿仙奴呢?<br />\n<br />\n#雲加又贏一仗<br />\n#雲爺爺<br />\n#請勿認真<br />\n#阿仙奴<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/29/193903_f82348a3d151e1afb17e40fed085dfee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F29%2F193903_f82348a3d151e1afb17e40fed085dfee.jpg&h=a03c7f50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68a6ce2e429f4aa98ecff14d65503a3981135f15","tid":646852,"uid":64863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T11:43:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e8d26408aee9c3fff13b203ac33de0035c5d25c","tid":646852,"uid":150618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T11:43:10.000Z","msg":"贏錢輸波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d27c1caf6e82210bf10063dbf0304351e56cff34","tid":646852,"uid":64863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e8d26408aee9c3fff13b203ac33de0035c5d25c","tid":646852,"uid":150618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T11:43:10.000Z","msg":"贏錢輸波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T11:52:57.000Z","msg":"唔準你咁講爺爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ce20c6e438f7c4864530ad0fb123a8f1aafe6c3","tid":646852,"uid":64863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T13:41:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}